hispanoamericana contempor&aacute;nea 1914-1970</EM>, Selecci&oacute;n,
pr&oacute;logo y notas de Jos&eacute; Olivio Jim&eacute;nez, Alianza
Editorial, Madrid, 1971. Copyright © of English translation
Johannes Beilharz 1981 / 2001. <I>Island in the Light</I> was
originally published in <I>Continental Drift, a journal of the
arts</I>, vol. 1, no. 1, spring 1982.</FONT></P>

